* &quot;The Candidate&quot; (published 1780)
* &quot;The Library&quot; (published 1781)
* &quot;The Village&quot; (published 1782)
* &quot;The Newspaper&quot; (published 1785)
* &quot;Poems&quot; (published 1807)
* &quot;The Borough&quot; (published 1810)
* &quot;Tales in Verse&quot; (published 1812)
